ine cover ms 40 and the future of feminism a panel discussion with feminist editors journalists and bloggers date & time thursday january 26 2012 3 00pm to 5 00pm description join us for an engaging conversation with six women who have helped define feminist journalism over the past 40 years read more location levinthal hall stanford humanities center 424 santa teresa st stanford ca 94305 gloria steinem headshot ms 40 and the future of feminism keynote address by gloria steinem date & time thursday january 26 2012 7 30pm to 9 00pm description the recording of gloria steinem's speech on january 26 can be listened to by going to the following link on the kzsu webpage http kzsunews tumblr com tagged speech read more location cemex auditorium knight management center stanford university 641 knight way stanford ca 94305 donate make a donation social links facebook twitter youtube scribd contact serra house 589 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8640 map 650 723 1994 gender email stanford edu
